ews</label>\n</p>\n<p>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T151_2\" name=\"Procedure\" />\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Clinical information\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Clinical information</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T151_8\" name=\"Clinical information\">Total hip arthroplasty. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Comparison\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Comparison</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T151_9\" name=\"Comparison\">None. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Findings\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Findings</header>\n<p>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T151_12\" name=\"Arthroplasty\" value=\"A total hip arthroplasty is present.\"/>\n</p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T151_13\">Alignment:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T151_14\" name=\"Alignment\" value=\"The prosthesis is in normal alignment.\"/></p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T151_19\">Complication:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T151_19\" name=\"Complication\" value=\"There is no evidence of loosening or fracture.\"/>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Impression\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Impression</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T151_20\" name=\"Impression\">Total hip arthroplasty in normal alignment. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
